channel.title: This section is private!
channel.description:
The polls and comments in this section are not to be discussed with anyone who would not usually have access to the section. That just leads to it getting back to whoever the poll is about, and that's never good.
Breaking this rule may result in losing your ability to view the vet sections. :)
